data.description: Professional photos will be uploaded on Friday the 12th.  Gorgeous Ellsworth Model in Gated Dominion Valley! You will feel welcomed the moment you step foot into this  2 story foyer.  The whole home has been freshly painted! Enjoy a formal dining room to your left and formal living room to your right.  The rear of the home features a Great Room with amazing windows and plantation shutters.  The open concept floor plan connects to your gourmet kitchen and morning room.  This floor is rounded off with an large office, laundry room and half bathroom.  Travel upstairs to the HUGE primary bedroom with attached primary bathroom. There is a bonus room attached to the primary suite that is great for an additional office or craft space! This floor is rounded off with 3 additional spacious bedrooms and another full bathroom.  The basement has endless opportunities to create the space you need! Enjoy all the wonderful amenities that DVCC has to offer, all while being near great schools, restaurants and multiple commuter routes!
